    <item>
      <title>特朗普称美国军方让公众对无人机保持“悬念”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-us-military-keeping-public-in-suspense-on-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普暗示美国政府知道新泽西州和纽约州神秘无人机目击事件的来源，这引发了人们对这些事件的质疑，因为联邦官员坚称没有证据表明存在安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-us-military-keeping-public-in-suspense-on-drones</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:30:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普不认为德桑蒂斯会任命儿媳担任参议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-doesn-t-see-desantis-appointing-daughter-in-law-to-senate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他不认为佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯会任命其儿媳拉拉·特朗普取代其提名的国务卿马尔科·卢比奥，代表该州进入美国参议院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-doesn-t-see-desantis-appointing-daughter-in-law-to-senate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将考虑赦免纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-he-d-consider-pardoning-nyc-mayor-eric-adams-m4ral0xp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将考虑赦免纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯，后者今年秋天因受贿和欺诈罪名被起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-he-d-consider-pardoning-nyc-mayor-eric-adams-m4ral0xp</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:11:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示愿意停止对 TikTok 的禁令，并软化立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-signals-openness-to-stopping-tiktok-ban-softening-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将研究是否避免对 TikTok Inc. 实施即将到来的禁令，此举扭转了他在 2020 年担任总统期间对这款中国视频分享应用采取的强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-signals-openness-to-stopping-tiktok-ban-softening-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言解雇不返回办公室的联邦雇员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-vows-to-fire-federal-employees-who-don-t-return-to-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁要解雇不回办公室的联邦雇员，并表示将向法庭挑战拜登政府的一项劳动合同，该合同规定了数千名联邦雇员的远程工作安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-vows-to-fire-federal-employees-who-don-t-return-to-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 16:57:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳瓦罗因总统记录问题被最高法院驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/navarro-turned-away-by-supreme-court-on-presidential-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝受理彼得·纳瓦罗的上诉，这位曾入狱的官员被当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命为他的贸易和制造业高级顾问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/navarro-turned-away-by-supreme-court-on-presidential-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 16:54:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长亚当斯在 2025 年竞选公共配套资金中落败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/nyc-s-adams-loses-bid-for-public-matching-funds-for-2025-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯的连任竞选遭遇沉重打击，因为该市的竞选财务委员会拒绝向他提供数百万美元的公共配套资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/nyc-s-adams-loses-bid-for-public-matching-funds-for-2025-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 15:43:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政政策与特朗普产生分歧 财政部长辞职 震惊加拿大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canadian-finance-minister-freeland-resigns-from-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 辞去了加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多内阁的职务，原因是双方在如何应对特朗普政府上台的问题上存在分歧，特朗普政府上台后，加拿大政府的核心受到了政治地震的震撼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canadian-finance-minister-freeland-resigns-from-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 14:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布加勒斯特市长宣布竞选罗马尼亚总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/bucharest-mayor-dan-to-run-for-romanian-presidency-g4media-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布加勒斯特市长尼库索·丹计划在明年的重新选举中以独立候选人身份竞选罗马尼亚总统，试图为对政治建制不满但又对复苏的极右翼保持警惕的公民提供另一种选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/bucharest-mayor-dan-to-run-for-romanian-presidency-g4media-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 10:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯阻止英国市长要求扩大税收权力的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/reeves-blocks-calls-from-english-mayors-for-more-tax-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 拒绝了英国市长们扩大其税收筹集能力的呼吁，这场冲突非常尴尬，因为就在政府提出将更多权力下放给地方领导人的​​计划之际。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/reeves-blocks-calls-from-english-mayors-for-more-tax-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
